Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Hydra shows "connection refused"

Solution: Verify target service is running with sudo systemctl status vsftpd or sudo systemctl status apache2
Issue: No results in output file

Solution: Check file permissions and ensure -o flag is used correctly. Verify credentials exist in wordlists.
Issue: Fail2Ban not blocking attacks

Solution: Check log paths in jail.local match actual log locations. Verify service is running with sudo fail2ban-client status
Issue: Scripts fail with permission errors

Solution: Ensure scripts are executable (chmod +x script.sh) and run with appropriate privileges
